query_name.0: How many inhabitants does the largest city in Canada have?
query_name.1: What is the population of Cairo?
query_name.2: How high is the Yokohama Marine Tower?
query_name.3: Which programming languages were influenced by Perl?
query_name.4: Give me all Australian nonprofit organizations.
query_name.5: Which ingredients do I need for carrot cake?
query_name.7: In which films did Julia Roberts as well as Richard Gere play?
query_name.9: Show me all basketball players that are higher than 2 meters.
query_name.10: How many films did Leonardo DiCaprio star in?
query_name.11: Give me all companies in the advertising industry.
query_name.12: How many movies did Park Chan-wook direct?
query_name.13: Who wrote the Game of Thrones theme?

dbpedia_query_raw.0: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?num WHERE { res:Canada dbo:largestCity ?city . ?city dbo:populationTotal ?num }
dbpedia_query_raw.1: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?pop WHERE { dbr:Cairo dbo:populationTotal ?pop }
dbpedia_query_raw.2: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?num WHERE { res:Yokohama_Marine_Tower dbo:height ?num }
dbpedia_query_raw.5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Carrot_cake dbo:ingredient ?uri }
dbpedia_query_raw.6: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?height WHERE { res:Claudia_Schiffer dbo:height ?height }
dbpedia_query_raw.7: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film ; dbo:starring res:Julia_Roberts ; dbo:starring res:Richard_Gere }
dbpedia_query_raw.8: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?film <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film> . ?film <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/producer> ?uri . } ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?film)) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
dbpedia_query_raw.11: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?c) WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Company> { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/industry> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertising> } UNION { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/industry> ?industry FILTER regex(?industry, "advertising", "i") } }
dbpedia_query_raw.13: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Game_of_Thrones dbo:composer ?uri }

dbpedia_query.0: SELECT DISTINCT ?num WHERE { dbr:Canada dbo:largestCity ?city . ?city dbo:populationTotal ?num }

dbpedia_query.4: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:type dbr:Nonprofit_organization { ?uri dbo:locationCountry dbr:Australia } UNION { ?uri dbo:location ?x . ?x dbo:country dbr:Australia } }

dbpedia_query.8: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?film rdf:type dbo:Film . ?film dbo:producer ?uri . } ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?film)) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

dbpedia_query.10: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?c) WHERE { ?uri a dbo:Film ; dbo:starring dbr:Leonardo_DiCaprio }
dbpedia_query.11: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?c) WHERE { ?uri a dbo:Company { ?uri dbo:industry dbr:Advertising } UNION { ?uri dbo:industry ?industry FILTER regex(?industry, "advertising", "i") } }
dbpedia_query.12: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri AS ?uri) WHERE { ?uri dbo:director dbr:Park_Chan-wook . }
